File: docs/content/docs/first-plugin.mdx — around lines 68-72.

Current code:
```typescript
async isReady(): Promise<boolean> {
  return false;
}
```

This makes the tutorial non-functional — the plugin will always report 'unavailable' and tool calls will fail. Change to:
```typescript
async isReady(): Promise<boolean> {
  // For production plugins, check if the user is authenticated.
  // Example: return document.querySelector('.logged-in-indicator') !== null;
  return true;
}
```

This makes the tutorial work out of the box while still guiding developers toward proper auth checks.
